VideoCrumb

An ncurses video manager. VideoCrumb keeps track of the shows you watch so
you don't have to.

Currently it has the bare minimum level of, mostly hardcoded, functionality.
Written in C++ and using some C++0x features.

Dependencies:
	ncurses
	boost
		filesystem

Tested with (x86_64):
  gcc 4.6
	GNU make 3.82
  boost 1.46
  ncurses 5.9

Known limitations:
	?	
